COMMANDS

/init-architecture
Create the initial modular structure for Django and Next.js.

/init-domain
Define models, services, selectors, endpoints, and UI flow for a domain.

/build-feature
Generate the backend and frontend code required for one feature.

/review-feature
Review implementation for bugs, architecture issues, and performance.

/debug-feature
Diagnose an issue and propose the minimal reliable fix.

/optimize-feature
Improve query efficiency, bundle size, caching, and maintainability.
